TITLE Advanced Weather Agent
#DEFINE CALL_WEATHER https://wttr.in

SAY Which city's weather would you like to check?
$city LISTEN
$weather_data CALL_WEATHER /{$city}?format=3
SAY Current Weather Info:
SAY {$weather_data}
IF the weather in {$city} is rainy or snowy:
  SAY Remember to bring an umbrella today!
ELSE:
  SAY Have a wonderful day outdoors!
